Package: oceanexplorer
Title: Explore our Planet's Oceans with NOAA
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    person(
     "Martin",  
     "Schobben", 
     email = "schobbenmartin@gmail.com", 
     role = c("aut", "cre"),
     comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8560-0037")
    )
Description: This package enables easy exploration of the NOAA WORLD OCEAN ATLAS. 
  It includes functions to extract NetCDF data from the repository and codes to 
  visualise several physical and chemical parameters of the ocean. A Shiny app
  further allows a more interactive exploration of the data.
